messageText.cn: 感谢你分享的蓝图。
messageText.en: Thank you for sharing the blueprint!

messageText.cn: 十分实用的蓝图！谢谢！
messageText.en: That's a really useful blueprint! Thank you!

messageText.cn: 请问有什么实用的蓝图吗？
messageText.en: Do you have any useful blueprints?

messageText.cn: 请试试这份蓝图，它或许能帮到你。
messageText.en: Try this blueprint. It might help you.

messageText.cn: 集成工业系统建设受阻，请求蓝图支援！
messageText.en: I can't finish my AIC Factory. Desperately need blueprints!

messageText.cn: 感谢你的蓝图支援！
messageText.en: Thank you for sharing the blueprint!

messageText.cn: 我的蓝图已经足够多了，感谢分享。
messageText.en: I've got more than enough blueprints. Thank you for sharing.

messageText.cn: 请问有什么有趣的留言信标吗？
messageText.en: Do you happen to have some interesting Memo Beacons?

messageText.cn: 感谢你的共享设备，这些已经足够了。
messageText.en: Thank you for sharing the facility. That's plenty enough.

messageText.cn: 可以推荐些其他共享设备吗？谢谢。
messageText.en: Do you have any other shared facilities to suggest? Thanks.

messageText.cn: 请问有什么便捷的共享设备吗？
messageText.en: Do you have any handy facilities to share?

messageText.cn: 请试试这个作战设备，它能高效对敌。
messageText.en: Try this combat facility. It's effective against enemies.

messageText.cn: 请试试这个作战设备，它是淤积点克星。
messageText.en: Try this combat facility. It's perfect for clearing Alluvia.

messageText.cn: 请试试这个滑索架，它能帮你赶路。
messageText.en: Try this Zipline Pylon. It makes traversal easier.

messageText.cn: 请试试这个滑索架，它能帮你便捷前往采集点。
messageText.en: Try this Zipline Pylon. It lets you get to a gathering point in no time.

messageText.cn: 请试试这个便捷存取站，它能帮你存取物品。
messageText.en: Try this Easy Stash. It's handy for storing and retrieving items.

messageText.cn: 请看看这个留言信标，它能指示隐藏物品。
messageText.en: Try this Memo Beacon. It reveals hidden items.

messageText.cn: 请看看这个留言信标，它很有趣。
messageText.en: Try this Memo Beacon. It looks interesting.

messageText.cn: 你好！
messageText.en: Good day!

messageText.cn: 我很期待！
messageText.en: I'll be waiting!

messageText.cn: 谢谢！
messageText.en: Thank you!

messageText.cn: 好久不见！
messageText.en: It's been a while!

messageText.cn: 辛苦了！
messageText.en: You did well!

messageText.cn: 再见。
messageText.en: Goodbye.

messageText.cn: 今天探索得开心吗？
messageText.en: Did you have fun exploring today?

messageText.cn: 很好！
messageText.en: Very well!

messageText.cn: 没问题！
messageText.en: No problem!

messageText.cn: 祝你万事顺遂。
messageText.en: I hope everything goes smoothly for you.

messageText.cn: 运送委托堆积成山，急需支援！
messageText.en: I've got loads of goods waiting to be delivered. Really need help!

messageText.cn: 前路艰险，运货困难，请求支援……
messageText.en: The roads are rough, and I can't manage the delivery alone. Please, someone help me...

messageText.cn: 感谢你完成了我的委托。
messageText.en: Thank you for getting the job done for me.

messageText.cn: 运送委托已完成，请查收调度券。
messageText.en: Delivery job completed. Here are your stock bills.

messageText.cn: 没能及时完成委托，真是抱歉。
messageText.en: Sorry I didn't get the goods delivered on time.

messageText.cn: 没能找到你的委托，抱歉。
messageText.en: Sorry I didn't find your job.

messageText.cn: 没关系，谢谢你愿意尝试我的委托。
messageText.en: It's okay, and thank you for trying to help.

messageText.cn: 委托确认！全速前进！
messageText.en: Job confirmed! Going full speed ahead!

messageText.cn: 舱室生产需要助力，请帮帮我。
messageText.en: My cabin needs production assist. Please help me.

messageText.cn: 感谢你来参加情报交流。
messageText.en: Thank you for taking part in the Clue Exchange.

messageText.cn: 感谢你的生产助力。
messageText.en: Thank you for the Production Assist.

messageText.cn: 感谢访问，欢迎再来。
messageText.en: Thank you for visiting. Come again soon!

messageText.cn: 会客室正在展开情报交流，快来参与吧。
messageText.en: The Reception Room has started a Clue Exchange. Join now.

messageText.cn: 尚缺一些线索，希望传递线索时替我留心。
messageText.en: I'm missing some clues. Please send them my way if you can.

messageText.cn: 我收集了许多蚀刻章，欢迎来会客室看看。
messageText.en: I earned new engraved medals. Check them out at my Reception Room.

messageText.cn: 我展示了新武器，欢迎来会客室看看。
messageText.en: I am showcasing new weapons. Check them out at my Reception Room.

messageText.cn: 我更新了干员履历，欢迎来会客室看看。
messageText.en: I updated the operator CVs. Check them out at my Reception Room.

messageText.cn: 我更新了陈列品，欢迎来中央环厅看看。
messageText.en: I've updated my display items. Check them out at my Reception Room.

messageText.cn: 今天弹性需求物资售价走高，欢迎来我的会客室的物资调度终端售卖。
messageText.en: Prices for elastic goods are going up. Stop by my Reception Room and sell some at the Stock Redistribution Terminal.

messageText.cn: 感谢你的线索。
messageText.en: Thank you for the Clue.
